<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT17">
<l>āla niḻaṟkī ḻaṟaneṟiyai nālvarkku</l>
<l>mēlai yukatturaittāṉ meyttavattōṉ ñāla</l>
<l>maḷantāṉai yāḻik kiṭantāṉai yālmēl</l>
<l>vaḷarntāṉait tāṉvaṇaṅku māṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In a former yuga, under the shade of a banyan tree,</l>
<l>[Śiva] with true penance told the four people about</l>
<l>the path of dharma that is his means of worshipping</l>
<l>Him who measured the worlds, Him who reclined on the sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who slept on the banyan [leaf].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
